            "Educate patients about sedation, orthostasis, and the distinction between low-dose sedative use vs. therapeutic antipsychotic dosing.",
            "Avoid using low-dose quetiapine as a primary treatment for chronic insomnia — behavioral therapies (CBT-I) should be first-line."
