              "explanation": "Quetiapine carries moderate-to-high metabolic risk including weight gain, dyslipidemia, and glucose dysregulation. It is not as metabolically burdensome as clozapine or olanzapine, but significantly more so than aripiprazole, lurasidone, or ziprasidone. Routine metabolic monitoring is required."
