            "Olanzapine has among the highest rates of weight gain and metabolic adverse effects of all antipsychotics — average weight gain of 4-4.5 kg in short-term trials.",
            "Despite metabolic concerns, olanzapine has consistently high efficacy ratings in head-to-head comparisons (CATIE: olanzapine outperformed all other SGAs).",
            "Olanzapine-samidorphan (Lybalvi) is a newer formulation designed to mitigate weight gain via opioid antagonism.",
            "IM olanzapine (Zyprexa Zydis or IM) is highly effective for acute agitation — but CONTRAINDICATED within 1 hour of IM lorazepam (respiratory depression risk).",
