            "Sertraline is the most commonly used SSRI overall — broad FDA approvals, good tolerability, and minimal CYP interactions.",
            "Fluvoxamine is a potent CYP1A2 and CYP3A4 inhibitor — dramatically raises clozapine and theophylline levels.",
            "SSRI sexual side effects (anorgasmia, decreased libido) affect up to 50-70% of patients — often underreported and undertreated.",
