              "type": "single",
              "stem": "An 80-year-old man is admitted for a urinary tract infection. On day 2, he becomes acutely confused, sees insects on the walls, and cannot state the date. He was cognitively intact at his last appointment 2 months ago. What is the MOST likely diagnosis?",
